  <entry>
    <title>Debian12 on LXC的硬件加速</title>
    <link href="/2025/02/08/Debian12%20on%20LXC%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/"/>
    <url>/2025/02/08/Debian12%20on%20LXC%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>环境介绍：<br>5.15.123 Kernel Version，Adreno 740，Debian12 on LXC</p><h1 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h1><h2 id="请确保你的源有deb-src-可以直接复制粘贴下面的"><a href="#请确保你的源有deb-src-可以直接复制粘贴下面的" class="headerlink" title="请确保你的源有deb-src(可以直接复制粘贴下面的)"></a>请确保你的源有deb-src(可以直接复制粘贴下面的)</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">deb http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm main contrib<br>deb http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm-updates main contrib<br>deb http://deb.debian.org/debian-security/ bookworm-security main contrib<br>deb-src http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm main contrib<br>deb-src http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm-updates main contrib<br>deb-src http://deb.debian.org/debian-security/ bookworm-security main contrib<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">apt build-dep mesa &amp;&amp; apt install git python3-pip python3-full curl -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/Danil/mesa/ -b turnip/feature/a7xx-basic-support --depth=1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="开始编译"><a href="#开始编译" class="headerlink" title="开始编译"></a>开始编译</h1><h2 id="首先我们要对源码打上两个补丁"><a href="#首先我们要对源码打上两个补丁" class="headerlink" title="首先我们要对源码打上两个补丁"></a>首先我们要对源码打上两个补丁</h2><p>(你问为什么？你可以尝试不打，然后后面就没法在termux-x11使用了)</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> mesa<br>curl -sL <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/termux/termux-packages/master/packages/mesa-vulkan-icd-freedreno-dri3/wsi-termux-x11.patch&quot;</span> | patch -p1<br>curl -sL <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/termux/termux-packages/master/packages/mesa-vulkan-icd-freedreno-dri3/tu_kgsl_export_dmabuf.patch&quot;</span> | patch -p1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">meson build/ -D prefix=/usr/ -D platforms=x11 -D gallium-drivers=zink,swrast -D vulkan-drivers=freedreno -D egl=enabled -D llvm=disabled  -D gles2=enabled -D glvnd=<span class="hljs-literal">true</span> -D glx=dri -D libunwind=disabled -D osmesa=<span class="hljs-literal">false</span> -D shared-glapi=enabled -D microsoft-clc=disabled -D valgrind=disabled -D gles1=disabled -D freedreno-kmds=msm,kgsl -Dbuildtype=release<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这一长串子看着有点吓人，你只管拷贝就行，hh</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">meson compile -C build/<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按下回车的瞬间，你的CPU核心不出意外就全被”拉满”了，期间可能会输出一些颜色，但是只要没有”Error”的字样，可以忽略掉的</p><h2 id="漫长地等待ing…"><a href="#漫长地等待ing…" class="headerlink" title="漫长地等待ing…"></a>漫长地等待ing…</h2><p>等它跑完进度(xxx&#x2F;xxx)后就停下来了，这时候可以安抚一下你发烫的手机(bushi)</p><h2 id="开始安装"><a href="#开始安装" class="headerlink" title="开始安装"></a>开始安装</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ninja -C build install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一长串字符飞速闪过，莫名还有点解压，hh</p><h2 id="使用方法"><a href="#使用方法" class="headerlink" title="使用方法"></a>使用方法</h2><p>至此，你已经安装好Mesa了。<br>但是，LXC它有点特殊，你还得手动挂载一下真机&#x2F;dev和termux的tmp目录。不过好办，只需要把下面的东西追加到&#x2F;data&#x2F;data&#x2F;com.termux&#x2F;files&#x2F;usr&#x2F;var&#x2F;lib&#x2F;lxc&#x2F;debian&#x2F;config文件即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">lxc.mount.entry = /data/data/com.termux/files/usr/tmp tmp none <span class="hljs-built_in">bind</span>,realtime,optional<br>lxc.mount.entry = /dev/dma_heap/ dev/dma_heap/ none <span class="hljs-built_in">bind</span>,create=<span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span> 0 0<br>lxc.mount.entry = /dev/kgsl-3d0 dev/kgsl-3d0 none <span class="hljs-built_in">bind</span>,optional,create=file<br>lxc.cgroup.devices.allow =<br>lxc.cgroup.devices.deny =<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="你又问为啥有两行空白的？这个可是用来解决超级玄学的报错哦！想复现？删掉它们，你就能得到报错了"><a href="#你又问为啥有两行空白的？这个可是用来解决超级玄学的报错哦！想复现？删掉它们，你就能得到报错了" class="headerlink" title="你又问为啥有两行空白的？这个可是用来解决超级玄学的报错哦！想复现？删掉它们，你就能得到报错了"></a>你又问为啥有两行空白的？这个可是用来解决超级玄学的报错哦！想复现？删掉它们，你就能得到报错了</h3><p>弄好之后记得重启一下LXC容器来使这个挂载生效。<br>接下来可以使用以下命令来测试：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#在Termux中:</span><br>termux-x11 :0 -ac<br><span class="hljs-comment">#在Debian12中:</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> DISPLAY=:0<br>MESA_LOADER_DRIVER_OVERRIDE=zink glmark2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到输出了自己的GPU型号即可代表成功啦！接下来打开termux-x11 APP就能看到窗口了</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
